            <li><strong>Lab 3:</strong> Real-time validation and form UX patterns <span class="badge text-bg-success">Current</span></li>
            <li><strong>Lab 4:</strong> Modals, confirm flows, history, pagination</li>
            <li><strong>Lab 5:</strong> Dynamic forms and long-running UX (polling)</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="alert alert-secondary mt-3 mb-0">
    Tip: Use <code>hx-trigger="keyup changed delay:500ms"</code> for debounced validation.
</div>
